# Zdravko's Personal Website

## About
Academic portfolio for a robotics researcher focused on tactile sensing.

## Website Structure
- `index.html` – Single-page portfolio
- `style/grid/` – Simple-grid CSS framework
- `assets/` – CV, profile image, favicon

## Index Structure
- Whole website is within the responsive simgle-grid structure. Support all device layouts (e.g. smartphone, tablet and workstation displays).
### Content
- name
- profile photo
- brief about paragraph
- link to the CV
- link to the Google Scholar page

## Style Guidelines
- **Tone**: Professional, academic, minimal
- **Font**: PT Serif (already loaded via Google Fonts)
- **Layout**: Simple-grid framework, keep it lightweight
- **HTML**: Semantic, accessible, no unnecessary complexity

## Code Conventions
- 4-space indentation
- Inline styles only for simple overrides; prefer CSS classes for reusable styles
- Keep the page fast and dependency-free

## Git Workflow
- Use conventional commits: `feat:`, `fix:`, `style:`, `docs:`
- Commit after completing coherent changes
- Test locally before pushing